Gaupol 0.20
===========

 [/] Migrate to Python 3, GTK+ 3, GNOME 3 and PyGI
     * Test encoding auto-detection
     * Check API documentation on aeidon.as_* and aeidon.is_*
     * Check decorator API documentation
     * Check if GtkSpell is available with PyGI support
     * Fix remaining regressions (search for 'XXX')
     * Check video toolbar spacing etc.
     * Check that interactive search works
     * Check dialog sizes
     * Check that clipboard is persistent
     * Migrate from Gtk.HBox and Gtk.VBox to Gtk.Box
     * Name text-assistant tree view to allow zebra-stripes
     * Check text-assistant layout due to new GTK+3 sidebar
     * Rename gaupol-plugin extension (and gaupol-bookmarks?)
     * Fix PyGObject constructors (usually no 'new')
 [/] Bump Python dependency to 3.2 or greater
 [/] Replace PyGTK dependency with PyGObject 3.0.0 or greater
 [/] Rewrite line-breaking algorithm to use a Knuth-Plass-style flexible
     system of penalties and a versatile measure of goodness
 [X] Add 48x48 and 256x256 pixel PNG icons and remove SVG icon
 [?] Move search history to configuration file
     * JSON should probably work better than ConfigObj did
 [X] Update Brazilian Portuguese translation
     (Átila Camurça, Darlildo Lima)
 [X] Update Hungarian translation (Andrássy László)

